square/power or involution (math.)/upright/honest/fair and square/direction/side/party (to a contract, dispute etc)/place/method/prescription (medicine)/just when/only or just/classifier for square things/abbr. for square or cubic meter

sentences.english: Simultaneously, categorical variables were compared with use of chi-square analysis.
sentences.chinese: 同時使用卡方分析比較分類變量。

sentences.english: The reduced chi-square statistic shows you when the fit is good.
sentences.chinese: 當擬合得很好時，你可以看到減少的卡方檢驗統計量。

sentences.english: Secondly, SPSS was used to do the Chi-square analysis to discuss whether there was any significant difference between the two grades.
sentences.chinese: 第二步則用卡方檢驗來討論兩個年級之間的區別。

sentences.english: All of the indexes are analyzed by Chi-square test except for the onset age which is analyzed by T test.
sentences.chinese: 除發病年齡採用t檢驗外，其餘變量均採用卡方檢驗。

sentences.english: The Six Sigma Black Belt will be able to perform chi-square analysis of contingency tables.
sentences.chinese: 六西格瑪黑帶應能完成關聯表的卡方分析。

sentences.english: Chi-square test is administered statistically to analysis the results.
sentences.chinese: 結果分析採用卡方檢驗。
